Description:
I was lucky enough to have the chance to work from Bali and in this video, I share some of the key aspects that I wish I knew before moving to one of the most amazing places on earth.

?ü§å SO WHAT

Here are some questions for you:

1. Do you enjoy having flexible working hours meaning that, for example, there will be days when you need to work in the morning and other days when you need to work in the evening?

2. Can you work with more extreme weather conditions (e.g. high humidity and temperatures)

3. Can you easily concentrate even when you don‚Äôt have your private space and you are often surrounded by people?

4. Can you comfortably handle inconveniences during the day given by external factors (like wifi connection issues or not perfect hygiene conditions?)

5. Do you have enough motivation and self-control to put work first even when there are plenty of fun activities and distractions around you?

6. Are you happy to leave family and friends for some time and create a new circle of connections from scratch?

if your answer is YES to most of these questions, then the digital nomad life might be for you and maybe something you should try one day‚Ä¶
